data.description: Fresh Water Pool Home on HUGE Triple Lot! Nestled in sunny SW Cape Coral this 3BR, 2BA encompasses 2210 sqft of living space overlooking the Aries Canal. Recent Updates in 2023 Include - New Metal Roof, Pool Screen, Gutters, Pool Tile & Coping, Fresh Interior and Exterior Paint & Travertine Floors Refreshed. Step inside & you are greeted by the warm open floor plan, formal dining, spacious den, shimmering travertine flooring & high ceilings. The kitchen w/granite countertops is complemented by newer stainless steel appliances, plentiful cabinet space & nook area overlooking the pool & canal. The master suite is a private retreat w/double vanities, a luxurious soaking jetted tub & custom-designed closets, perfectly accentuated by the oversized walk-in shower. Outdoor living here is nothing short of spectacular. The expansive screened-in lanai invites you to unwind in the shade while overlooking the pavered pool area & canal. Dive into the heated pool, complete with mesmerizing waterfall feature & let the worries of the world wash away. Finally the oversized lot can be utilized as dog yard, kid play area OR dream big & build your own extended RV/toy garage in the future! Call today!
